ujarat]].<ref>{{cite book |url=http://www.ncbc.nic.in/Pdf/gujarat.pdf |title=Central List of OBCs for the State of Gujarat |page=5 |publisher=National Commission for Backward Classes |date=|accessdate=18 May 2016}}</ref> *[[Haryana]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://censusindia.gov.in/Tables_Published/SCST/dh_sc_haryana.pdf|format=PDF|title=Haryana : DATA HIGHLIGHTS : THE SCHEDULED CASTES : Census of India 2001 |website=Censusindia.gov.in|accessdate=7 October 2017}}</ref> *[[Himachal Pradesh]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ncbc.nic.in/Pdf/himachalpradesh.pdf|title=National Commission for Backward Classes|website=Ncbc.nic.in|accessdate=7 October 2017}}</ref> *[[Jharkhand]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://censusindia.gov.in/Tables_Published/SCST/dh_sc_jharkhand.pdf|format=PDF|title=Jharkhand : DATA HIGHLIGHTS: THE SCHEDULED CASTES : Census of India 2001|website=Censusindia.gov.in|accessdate=7 October 2017}}</ref> *[[Karnataka]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ncbc.nic.in/Pdf/karnataka.pdf|title=National Commission for Backward Classes|website=Ncbc.nic.in|accessdate=7 October 2017}}</ref> *[[Madhya Pradesh]].<ref>{{cite book |url=http://www.ncbc.nic.in/Pdf/madhyapradesh.pdf |title=Central List of OBCs for the State of Madhya Pradesh |page=5 |publisher=National Commission for Backward Classes |date= |accessdate=18 May 2016}}</ref> *[[Maharashtra]].<ref>{{cite book |url=http://www.ncbc.nic.in/Pdf/maharashtra.pdf |title=Central List of OBCs for the State of Maharashtra |page=4 |publisher=National Commission for Backward Classes |date= |accessdate=18 May 2016}}</ref> *[[Odisha]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://censusindia.gov.in/Tables_Published/SCST/dh_sc_orissa.pdf|format=PDF|title=Orissa : DATA HIGHLIGHTS : THE SCHEDULED CASTES : Census of India 2001|website=Censusindia.gov.in|accessdate=7 October 2017}}</ref> *[[Puducherry]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ncbc.nic.in/Pdf/puducherry.pdf|title=National Commission for Backward Classes|website=Ncbc.nic.in|accessdate=7 October 2017}}</ref>